I & = & PQ_{0}+R_{1}\\
P & = & R_{1}Q_{1}+R_{2}\\
R_{1} & = & R_{2}Q_{2}+R_{3}\\
\vdots\\
R_{l} & = & R_{l+1}Q_{l+1}+R_{l+2}\\
\vdots\\
R_{t-1} & = & R_{t}Q_{t}
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
Обозначение: 
\begin_inset Formula $I\left(x\right)=Iir\left[v,\mathbb{Q},x\right]\in F$
